<https://www.metaconceptualart.com/data/linked-art/priority-live-auction-2009> <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P190_has_symbolic_content> "Sun & Rain Works asserts documented prior evidence that, on March 30, 2009, the act of Sotheby's Photographs auction itself was designated as a Metaconceptual Art work (The Auction as Artwork), realized through two artifact-parts created live: www.wtfisart.com and WTF is Ansel Adams. Taken together, the artwork records, the appropriated auction event, the shared creation act, and the privately held evidence archive establish documented priority for treating a live auction as artwork. Consistent with the project's comparison and priority policy, this statement does not name, compare against, or dispute any later artist or event, and asserts no influence, contact, or derivation absent separately published evidence." .
