_:r14b3 <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P190_has_symbolic_content> "The public Sotheby's Photographs auction held on March 30, 2009, carried out by Sotheby's. Sun & Rain Works designates the act of this auction as the material of the metaconceptual work The Auction as Artwork. This record names the appropriated real-world event; it does not assert that Sotheby's authored, endorsed, or participated in the artwork." .
