_:r15b3 <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P190_has_symbolic_content> "International auction house founded in 1744. Named here only as the institution that carried out the Sotheby's Photographs auction on March 30, 2009 — the public event that Sun & Rain Works designates as the material of the metaconceptual work The Auction as Artwork. Recording Sotheby's as the auction's host asserts no partnership, endorsement, or claim against Sotheby's." .
