_:r3b1 <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P190_has_symbolic_content> "concept:metaconceptual-art" .
_:r3b1 <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P2_has_type> <http://vocab.getty.edu/aat/300312355> .
_:r3b1 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E42_Identifier> .
_:r3b2 <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P190_has_symbolic_content> "Art that treats art, its institutions, markets, archives, and viewers as the material of the work. A self-defined movement concept created by Sun & Rain Works in 2007, extending conceptual art into the system that makes art legible. Its public Record argues credibility through genealogy, defined principles, works on view, machine-readable standards, external alignment, and provenance over time." .
_:r3b2 <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P2_has_type> <http://vocab.getty.edu/aat/300435416> .
_:r3b2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E33_Linguistic_Object> .
